    "body": "Actually, this isn't as bad as I was thinking.  It's be almost like resampling, the one expensive op you'd have to do is generate the range of anchored dates. \n`rng = pd.date_range(df.index.min(), df.index.max(), freq=day)`\n\nThen you'd just need a cython function that generates window edges from that range and the frame's index.\n"
